<@U2H3TT8F2> Would you mind letting us know if you have any updates here?

We are working on updating our theme with the new requirements as well. We were preparing to launch the newer version today but the validation tool just gave us even more issues/errors that we need to fix (including the brand settings requirement <@U03AKL6Q1B2> talked about).

What happens if we can't get our updated version published today? :thinking_face:
Its ok if you cant get the updated version today. There should be an email going out to you tomorrow with more information on this.
<@U2H3TT8F2> Perfect. Thank you so much for your help!
